column5: Anyone know if a 2006 Navionics Premium Hotmaps chip has Lac Seul on it?
Yes. I have the Dec 2006 Canada Premium Hotmaps chip by Navionics and it does have Lac Suel.KT
Just an FYI as posted on here before. The Navionics North also has Lac Suel on it. I have both chips and the Lac Suel information is identical on both.
